{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_09_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 2話 代打、佐伯遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後、代打の仕事現場",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later at substitute work place",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんの代打で来ました！\nサニーピースの佐伯遙子です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm here as Rei-chan's substitute!\nI'm Haruko Saeki from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9689793665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.4181859254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "今日はバンバン、クイズに答えていきますよ～！\nよろしくお願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I'm going to answer all the quizzes~!\nPlease treat me well~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.0358507076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（初めての現場だけど、落ち着いているな）\n（これなら、安心して見ていられそうだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is her first time here‚ but she's calm.）\n（I think I can watch her with peace of mind.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2691841204,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_quiz-button-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14430.8158796,
          "startTime": 30.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.1025173584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "次の問題は～……あ、これなら分かるわ！\n早押し早押し早押し、えいえいえいえいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next question is~… Ah‚ I know this one!\nBuzzer buzzer buzzer‚ ei ei ei ei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333334049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（お！　遙子さんが回答権をゲット！）\n（ここで答えれば逆転だ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh! Haruko-san got the chance to answer!）\n（If she gets this right‚ it's a comeback!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.49607745,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10603.92255,
          "startTime": 45.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.8294105767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "やったわ！　答えは～、答えは～、あの～、なんだっけ\nあ～！？　待って！　ごめんなさ～～い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did it! The answer is~‚ the answer is~‚ uh~‚ what was it?\nAh!? Wait! I'm sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.6151933589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（こ、答えをど忘れしてる……）\n（めちゃくちゃMCの人にイジられてるぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（S-She forgot the answer…）\n（She's being teased so much by the host.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5151935655,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_quiz-button-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11018.139767800008,
          "startTime": 64.5333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_correct-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14851.4731012,
          "startTime": 68.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.7151933589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "う～、次こそ……あ！　この曲分かるわ！\nはいはいはーい！　答えは、『あゝ星見坂』ですっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh~‚ next time… Ah! I know this song!\nYes yes yes~! The answer is \"Ah Ah Hoshimi Hill\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（イントロクイズで演歌を一発正解……！？）\n（ベテランのタレントさんも戸惑った顔をしてるぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She got the enka song right on the first try in the intro quiz… !?）\n（Even the veteran entertainer looks confused.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7033117054,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7596.6882946,
          "startTime": 79.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8699781654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "え、年齢ですか？　サバ読んだりなんてしてませんよ～\n正真正銘、大学生です。留年もしてませんってば～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ age? I'm not lying about my age~.\nI'm a genuine‚ real college student. I haven't even failed a year~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3947423511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5539915003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（ま、またイジられてる……）\n（でも大御所の人に、名前を覚えてもらえてるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's being teased again…）\n（But at least the big-shot remembers her name.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2164790404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これはもしかして……\n右と左のここを斜めのここと入れ替えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ could this be…?\nSwitching this part on the right and left with this diagonal part…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1000000716,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_incorrect-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6814.218091600012,
          "startTime": 102.9142181632
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9142181632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "えー！？　違いましたか？\nで、でもまだまだ、最後まで頑張りましょうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~! Was I wrong?\nB-But still‚ let's do our best until the end!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（他の出演者の方とのコミュニケーションもバッチリだ）\n（正解率はともかく、いい雰囲気で進んでいるぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Communication with the other performers is perfect.）\n（Regardless of the correct answer rate‚ the atmosphere is good.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5064176636,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5466.666666699993,
          "startTime": 121.9730843303
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.4230841236
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.4230841236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、お疲れ様です\n番組大盛り上がりでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ good work.\nThe show was a lot of fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7064176636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……恥ずかしいわ。怜ちゃんみたいに\nもっと正解出来れば良かったんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ ahaha… I'm embarrassed. I wish I could have\ngotten more answers right‚ like Rei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2666682642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.5911358751
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "現役大学生なのに、お馬鹿キャラが定着しちゃったら\nどうしよう。学業をおろそかに～とか言われちゃうかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if I‚ a current college student‚ get stuck with a dumb image?\nWhat should I do? I might be told that I'm neglecting my studies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1666682642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.6876438693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "クイズと勉強は別ですから、大丈夫ですよ\nそれに遙子さんも正解してたじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quizzes and studying are separate things‚ so it's okay.\nBesides‚ you got some answers right‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.287644076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "イントロクイズね\n演歌とか、昔の曲とか、家族が好きで聴いてたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The intro quiz.\nEnka and old songs‚ my family likes to listen to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4333349308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.2117484963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、普段と違うお仕事をするのも楽しいわね\n明日も、レギュラーの仕事と代打、両方とも頑張るわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ it's fun to do something different from usual.\nI'll do my best at both my regular and the substitute job tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.0333349308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.546351774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュールがきつかったら\n遠慮なく言って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If your schedule is too tight‚\nplease don't hesitate to tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.079685314,
      "sfxList": []
